# Compatibility note:
# This repo now tracks `apps/web/.env` directly for zero-config startup.
# Keep shared defaults in `.env`, not in this file.
#
# This file intentionally stays comment-only to avoid duplicated config sources.
# If a workflow expects an example file, use:
# - `.env` as the base defaults reference
# - `.env.dev.example` / `.env.prod.example` as overlay references
# - `.env.local.example` / `.env.*.local.example` for secret overrides
